{
  "id": 4411,
  "name": "Dongsheng",
  "desc": "<p>The owner of Second Life. He used to be an avid adventurer but was later seriously injured in an accident in Dihua Marsh. After being saved by Xiao and narrowly escaping death, he has since retired as an adventurer and decided to open a shop under the name \"Second Life\" as a commemoration of that fateful event.</p>",
